Title: Gnome Alone
Writer: Robert Moreland (screen story by), Michael Schwartz (screenplay by), Zina Zaflow (screenplay by), Jared Micah Herman (based on the story by), Kyle Newman (based on the story by)
Actors: Becky G, Josh Peck, Tara Strong, Olivia Holt
Plot: When Chloe discovers that her new home's garden gnomes are not what they seem, she must decide between the pursuit of a desired high school life and taking up the fight against the Troggs.
